data.description:
****BACK ON THE MARKET DUE TO NO FAULT OF THE SELLER****
***PRICE IMPROVEMENT ALONG WITH $5,000 SELLER CREDIT****

MOVE IN READY! This delightful residence features 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. The open living room seamlessly connects to the kitchen, creating a welcoming and inclusive atmosphere. The kitchen has lots of cabinet space, large island and granite countertops. Flex room on main level can be used for home office or workout area. Spacious owner's suite on second level, with dual vanity, walk-in shower and garden tub. Spacious secondary bedrooms for guests. Backyard is perfect for entertaining and features an oversize deck. Nestled in a thriving subdivision Austen Lakes, built in 2020, this home ensures modern conveniences and contemporary aesthetics. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful property yours!
